If MAP estimation is performed, we obtain  an adaptable step-size LMS estimation

\begin{equation}
{\bf w}_{k}^{(LMS)} = {\bf w}_{k-1}^{(LMS)} + \eta_k (y_k - {\bf x}_k^T {\bf w}_{k-1}^{(LMS)}){\bf x}_k, 	
